                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The Hellknights draw or reload their longbows, then launch a ranged attack in the form of a volley. This volley is a @Template[type:burst|distance:10] within 100 feet that deals @Damage[(3d8+2)[piercing]|options:area-damage] damage (@Check[reflex|dc:23|basic|options:area-effect] save). When the troop is reduced to 2 or fewer segments, this area decreases to a @Template[type:burst|distance:5].</p>"
                },
